Package: pRojects
Title: One-Liners to Setup R Projects
Version: 0.0.1.9003
Description: Setting up R project directories for teaching,
    presenting, analysis, package development can be a pain. pRojects
    shortcuts this by creating folder structures and setting good defaults
    for you.
